      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Pawel Koziol</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:232px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nescitus\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/88/PawelKoziol.jpg\" width=\"230\" height=\"230\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:PawelKoziol.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Pawel Koziol <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Pawel Koziol</b>,<br />\nan amateur chess programmer from Poland. Author of <a href=\"/Hopeless\" title=\"Hopeless\">Hopeless</a> (open-source, written in <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>, characterized by very unbalanced playing style) and <a href=\"/CCCP\" title=\"CCCP\">CCCP</a> (free but closed source, derived from <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a>, playing also <a href=\"/Games#ChessVariants\" title=\"Games\">chess variant</a> called <a href=\"/Knightmate_Chess\" title=\"Knightmate Chess\">knightmate</a>). \nPawel Koziol has contributed to the <a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Chess Programming Wiki</a> mainly to the pages on <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a>. He is co-author ofthe <a href=\"/CPW-Engine\" title=\"CPW-Engine\">CPW-engine</a> and is author of <a href=\"/Glass\" title=\"Glass\">Glass</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and the more recent open source engine <a href=\"/Rodent\" title=\"Rodent\">Rodent</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=17361\">is there a 10x8 equivalent of 0x88</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18081\">fractal null move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 28, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=21516\">PVS and aspiration</a>  by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 31, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/PVS_and_Aspiration\" title=\"PVS and Aspiration\">PVS and Aspiration</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41590\">open source gift for Christmas</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 25, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42687\">Rodent 0.12</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 29, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46686\">Rodent 0.17 for New Year!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 31, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47250\">positional patterns for \"human\" engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation_Patterns\" title=\"Evaluation Patterns\">Evaluation Patterns</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47417\">Rodent turns 1.0&#160;!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49517\">Rodent 1.1 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 30, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50840\">Piece/square table challenge</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50988\">Rodent 1.3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54802\">fixing CPW-engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55477\">pattern coding in bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Defended_Pawns_(Bitboards)#DefendedDefenders\" title=\"Defended Pawns (Bitboards)\">Defended Defenders</a>, <a href=\"/Pawn_Chain\" title=\"Pawn Chain\">Pawn Chain</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57805\">Mini Rodent asks for code review</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58052\">Mini Rodent 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2015 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59257\">Rodent II is out</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66042\">OpenTal - almost new engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66248\">OpenTal 1.1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Jan 05, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67524\">Poor man's neurones</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 21, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68278&amp;start=2\">Lazy SMP ideas</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68343\">Rodent III 0.273 - official release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2018 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72030\">Eval hashtable replacement scheme</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation_Hash_Table\" title=\"Evaluation Hash Table\">Evaluation Hash Table</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://prodeo.actieforum.com/t118-my-statement-from-rodent-homepage\">My statement from Rodent homepage</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pawel Koziol</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">ProDeo Forum</a>, December 05, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://prodeo.actieforum.com/t120-engine-choosing-between-sets-of-piece-square-tables\">Engine choosing between sets of piece/square tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">nescitus</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">ProDeo Forum</a>, December 05, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://prodeo.actieforum.com/t123-controlled-randomness-of-evaluation-function\">Controlled randomness of evaluation function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">nescitus</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">ProDeo Forum</a>, December 06, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://prodeo.actieforum.com/t252-little-fun-with-tscp\">little fun with TSCP</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">nescitus</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">ProDeo Forum</a>, February 12, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a>, <a href=\"/PeSTO%27s_Evaluation_Function\" title=\"PeSTO&#39;s Evaluation Function\">PeSTO's Evaluation Function</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/nescitus\">nescitus (Pawel Koziol) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pkoziol.cal24.pl/rodent/rodent.htm\">Rodent Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pkoziol.cal24.pl/opental/\">OpenTal 1.1</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawel_Koziol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/nescitus\">nescitus (Pawel Koziol) · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pkoziol.cal24.pl/glass/\">Glass Homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pkoziol.cal24.pl/rodent/rodent.htm\">Rodent Chess</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68154&amp;start=7\">Re: Lazy SMP and 44 cores</a> by <a href=\"/John_Stanback\" title=\"John Stanback\">John Stanback</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Wasp\" title=\"Wasp\">Wasp</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301072535\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 87/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 178/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4783-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301072535 and revision id 23946\n -->\n"
